{"tid":960530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這日本女生正到讓中國人不想抗日　只要AV女優","createTime":"2018-12-29T13:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T14:33:18.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e49eec014a54e6d7c2143d96afb87f9b26ccdb2","tid":960530,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:22:19.000Z","msg":"中國人一邊喊抗日、一邊遊日本幫日本發大財，這一點都不稀奇，不過有位日本女生實在正到讓中國人，都不想抗日了！<br />\n<br />\n中國微博網友近日分享一段影片，表示有群中國妹子到日本旅遊，到前來服務的日本女服務生更是亮點。當中國女生用中文討論事情時，這位日本女服務生因為語言的問題，無法聽懂所有中文對話，只能站在一旁。但她又正又呆萌的表情，融化了不少中國網友，中國網友紛紛直呼：「好可愛。」、「這個服務員漂亮。」還有網友直接聯想到日本AV女優吉澤明步，說兩人外型相似度極高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RupEFvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRupEFvp.png&h=76851410&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e48c56c3d9afbe51ff0eeee87cba088f087451f","tid":960530,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:23:28.000Z","msg":"分享一段影片<br />\n<br />\n10"},{"pid":"1e31479538e5e739c583f39d5f7f05f79e64109d","tid":960530,"uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e48c56c3d9afbe51ff0eeee87cba088f087451f","tid":960530,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:23:28.000Z","msg":"分享一段影片<br />\n<br />\n10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"中國微博"},{"pid":"7edecbbad222d16f685bbd93ef6666052913cd08","tid":960530,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"日本周街影人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629e38469469724fa8a1174215167515509497f6","tid":960530,"uid":162535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"fyi 日本偷拍係犯法"}]}